{"tid":1806584,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"班狗話無破壞匯豐, 咁我地更加要承認係示威者做","createTime":"2020-01-01T11:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T12:04:10.000Z","uid":47565,"like":19,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5cb8ee78a338626cf652ea242915a31fb09a8885","tid":1806584,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T11:14:11.000Z","msg":"依加班狗唔認係便衣狗做 正中下懷<br />\n即係示威者話自己係警察就走得甩<br />\n咁會帶出幾個問題同後果:<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>狗方縱容暴徒逃走</strong></span><br />\n到時藍絲就會屌班狗辦事不力<br />\n放走示威者<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>狗方對便衣狗無任何記認</strong></span><br />\n暴露出現時班便衣狗嘅行動無任何合理性<br />\n證明過住charge手足打便衣狗嘅案, D手足無可能知佢係警察 =&gt; 襲警不成立<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>順便宣傳點解要裝修匯豐</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n就算之後班狗反口, 認係便衣狗,<br />\n咁只會令佢嘅公信力(對藍絲而言)更加低<br />\n同埋承認佢地主動製造混亂<br />\n到時再幫佢國際宣傳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地係立於不敗之地!!!!!<br />\n</span></span><br />\n要煲大佢<br />\n<br />\n下面開放討論"},{"pid":"c0d1846dec3432223ecf81970dc1033a2b7d1ee4","tid":1806584,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T11:14:38.000Z","msg":"［置頂］20:00 和你Shop x 黃圈：開飯啦！元旦促銷大減價 ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1806464\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1806464</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8356df7ccc3655413592de27b0c19a05607cbabc","tid":1806584,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T11:18:01.000Z","msg":"匯豐自己申請嘅<br />\n佢最重視嘅野咁就無左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你同黑警合作得就預左啦<br />\n<br />\n保一間無十間，值咩？傻鳩高層"},{"pid":"8f9618be7f9af29c1c05992d2339119a43e7ca7a","tid":1806584,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T11:18:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4b42ad7ac35d13ff49bf82379259821edf84411b","tid":1806584,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T11